# Testing

- **Run:** `npm test` (`NODE_OPTIONS=--experimental-vm-modules`)
- **Stack:** Jest + Supertest; import app from `#src/app.js` (no server listen)
- **Coverage:** `coverage/` — gitignored; CI uploads artifact (30 days)

## CI test env

```
NODE_ENV=test
NODE_OPTIONS=--experimental-vm-modules
DATABASE_URL=postgres://test:test@localhost:5432/test?sslmode=disable  # or secret
JWT_SECRET=test-jwt-secret
ARCJET_KEY=... 
ARCJET_ENV=development
```

## Assertions

404 routes must expect:

```javascript
expect(response.body).toHaveProperty('error', 'Not Found');
expect(response.body).toHaveProperty('message', 'Route not found');
```

Commit `tests/` source; never commit `coverage/`.
